s, it was corrected to \"የማይገባለት\" (root: መግባት - to be fitting/proper).\n*   \"የሚመሰክን\" was corrected to \"የሚመሰክር\" (root: መመስከር - to testify), as 'መሰከነ' is not a recognized Amharic verb.\n*   \"እክፍልሽ\" was corrected to \"እከፍልሽ\" (root: መክፈል - to pay/divide), as 'ክፍል' (part) would not fit the verbal context of surrounding words.\n*   \"ለብሸሽ\" was visually corrected to \"ለብሰሽ\" (replacing ሸሽ with ሰሽ for standard Amharic morphology).\n*   \"ከቆዬሽ\" was visually corrected to \"ከቆየሽ\" (replacing ዬ with የ for standard Amharic morphology).\n*   \"የኤክስቴሽኑን\" was visually corrected to \"ኤክስቴንሽን\" (standard spelling for 'extension').\n\nAll single-character words or roots were filtered out, ensuring all included entries meet the minimum length requirement. The Part of Speech tagging was strictly limited to the specified major categories.","input_words":["እንደሚገባዉ","በሄራልድ","አለመደረጋቸውና","ቀብረናታል","ያስገዝባል","የማይገቃለት","ተጀምሬ","የሚመሰክን","እንደሚለሱ","ከማመንጫው","ለፔፕሲው","የጣልኳቸው","በረከትሽን","ጠይቆዋት","በአቶነቱ","ያታግለናል","የኤክስቴሽኑን","ከእነስህተቱ","ከእነጥፋቱ","የቆራጦች","የማኅበረሰባቸው","ቢያዝንማ","ሊያስጨርሰን","እንከልሳቸው","የብሄርተኝነቱና","እክፍልሽ","ለብሸሽ","ደርበሽ","ከቆዬሽ","ስትደፋፈሪ"],"batch_number":154,"batch_label":"Words 4591-4620 (Batch 154/667)","model_version":null},{"id":"46cf1a13-88db-401c-93bc-f6e961670923","created_at":"2026-03-04T09:41:53.992921+00:00","word":null,"source_file":"rare_words_16/chunk_0624.txt","batch_index":0,"words":[{"pos":"Noun","root":"ታይወድሪ","word":"ታይወድሪ","synonyms":["Taiwodri"],"importance":5},{"pos":"Noun","root":"አይሱዚ","word":"አይሱዚዎች","synonyms":["Isuzu vehicles","Isuzus"],"importance":6},{"pos":"Adverb","root":"አሁን","word":"አሁን","synonyms":["now","at present","currently"],"importance":8},{"pos":"Verb","root":"መምጣት","word":"አስኪመጣ","synonyms":["until he comes","until it comes","when he comes"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Verb","root":"ማበድ","word":"እንዳያብድ","synonyms":["lest he go mad","so that he doesn't go mad"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Verb","root":"መለማመድ","word":"ሳይለምደው","synonyms":["before he gets used to it"